# Prettier reformats markdown tables in .mdx files in ways that break them
# (e.g. inserts pipe separators inside `|x − y|` cell contents, treating them
# as column dividers). Markdown is hand-formatted in this project. Keep
# Prettier off everything under site/docs/ and any top-level result READMEs.
site/docs/**/*.mdx
site/docs/**/*.md
results/**/*.md
README.md
CONTRIBUTORS.md

# Prettier also re-indents YAML (2-space -> 4-space) and pads list brackets
# in GitHub Actions workflows. Keep it off CI definitions.
.github/**/*.yml
.github/**/*.yaml

# CITATION.cff is a YAML file with a strict schema; don't let Prettier touch it.
CITATION.cff
